text: is a fictional character in the Resident Evil survival horror video game series. Ethan was introduced as one of the playable characters of the 2017 video game Resident Evil 7: Biohazard. He is also the protagonist of the 2021 video game Resident Evil Village. ==References== Category:Resident Evil characters Category:Fictional American people Category:Fictional characters introduced in the 2010s
